BuyNefiToken(uint256).details: Facilitates the purchase of Nefi Tokens.

params.amountIn: The amount of DEOD Tokens to stake.

allowance(address,address).details: Returns the remaining number of tokens that `spender` will be allowed to spend on behalf of `owner` through {transferFrom}. This is zero by default. This value changes when {approve} or {transferFrom} are called.

balanceOf(address).details: Returns the value of tokens owned by `account`.

claimTokens(uint256).details: Allows users to claim their tokens based on their eligibility.

params.amount: The amount of tokens the user is eligible to claim.

sellNefiToken(uint256).details: Facilitates the purchase of Nefi Tokens.

params.amountIn: The amount of NEFI Tokens to sell and get the DEOD acc. to price - platform fee.

totalSupply().details: Returns the value of tokens in existence.
